===Adjective===
'''bland'''

# [[mild|Mild]]; [[soft]]; [[gentle]]; [[smooth]] and [[soothing]] in manner; suave; as, a bland temper; bland persuasion; a bland sycophant.
# Having soft and soothing qualities; not drastic or irritating; not stimulating; as, a bland oil; a bland diet.

